cmpReviews: Management truly wants to hear our input and makes continuous improvements. Some of us work on individual client projects, some are in teams.  The engineers are dedicated and professional.  Many have a work hard, play hard mentality.  You are encouraged to take on projects and responsibilities if you are up for it.  I like the culture.It's cool that they stock the office with nice breakfast bars and drinks.Work is 8am to 5pm in the office, some remote..Bringing your "A" game is a must.Co-workers are pretty cool.
